			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Right Kick:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Left Punch:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Left Kick:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Charge:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Hold any Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Roll opponent on ground:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad down + Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Attack opponent on ground:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad down + Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Throw:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square + X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Unique ability:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle + Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Taunt:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square + Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Run:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Press forward two times</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Vibration on / off:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font><br>
